data.description: This cape cod home is a 3 bedroom with 2 bathrooms and is located in a great area near downtown Hebron. The main level has a large living room. dining room area and main floor bedroom. The kitchen has 42'' kitchen cabinets and has been slightly updated. The upstairs has 2 large bedrooms with large closets. This home has a full basement for a large recreation area or extra storage. The large backyard is fenced in with a pool. This home has low Porter County taxes. This is a must see!
